message.body: There's a picture of you as a baby....and I am OBSESSED with it. Haha. You're so cute!!!
Awesome! You a free lady! And waahhh?? Whatchu doing staring at pictures of me as a little?? Put that away haha. Gonna make me blush. Youuuu the cute one
Seriously. OBSESSED. I saved it onto my phone and kept looking at it.
Where on earth did you get a baby picture?! Haha
Your cousin posted it on facebook and tagged you in it.
Oh my. I have never seen that picture..honored to be included in such a moment ha. Guess im next for engagement. Wanna help me with that? And... meet grandma :)
Yeahhhhh. Haha. Although, how can I meet your grandma? You were so chunky :D I love it.
Naw i mean in the picture. Not too many pix of her. Dunno if you knew what she looked like..And yes hehe, i possessed mad chunk :-p Tw'ere happy days :)
Ahh. I see! I did not know what she looked like. Mad chunk. I love it.
Tho ... seems i missed the moment in this particular picture to look happy haha
And now I'm going to bed! Haha. I love you.
Haha and i am waking up! :) Love YOU. Sweet dreams, my darling. Kiss you
Good morning, beautiful! Just wanted to let you know that your bday also kicks off spring break for us too :-D No class from 6th-16th!!!!
